name: Basic Transcribing
title: Transcribing audio
instructions:
• Listen to the audio and transcribe the content into the text field area.

  • If there is MORE than a single speaker, make sure to use SpeakerX: where X is the speaker's number.
  • Audio cannot be transcribed at all? Enter N/A in the text field.

  • An example for a single-speaker should be:
  • Hello, my name is...


  • An example for a multi-speakers audio should be:
  • Speaker1: Hello
  • Speaker2: Good morning.
  • Speaker1: How are you today?
    • Speaker3: Hello
    Speaker2: Hey
    Speaker1: Hey
work_unit_html: Update Required To play the media you will need to either update your browser to a recent version or update your Flash plugin.
